hopobject.body: How much will it cost to send this letter to ? augmentation du prix du gasoil au maroc 2014 The fall in oil futures follows a rally in both benchmarksto multi-month highs above $109 in mid-July, which attractedbullish speculators and large hedge funds into the market. U.S.crude in particular had rallied to a 16-month high asinfrastructure developments allowed oil in landlocked Cushing,Oklahoma, the delivery point for U.S. futures, to flow to theU.S. coasts.
